Member

Class Member

  • java.lang.Object
    • Member.Member

  • public class Member
extends java.lang.Object
    Member class is the class that represents all the information about the member registred if the system, mainly: The username of the user The password of the user The balance if the user the community in which the user is enrolled in The profile of the user
    See Also:
    Community, Profile
